1.12
log
@big changes.

- capitalise the chipset names since thats what the manufacturer uses.
- lowercase b in 802.11b because thats what ieee uses.
- dont lie about supporting hostap and adhoc demo modes.
- better descriptions of what the hardware can do, especially the operating
modes.
- replace the ifconfig examples with real documentation what options are
used to configure operation of the interface
- list caveats

lots and lots of help from and ok jmc@@
